c: 20
v: 86
t: "Mana Musa nakalukha khu Bandu bebe nasinyishe nabeelele. Naboola mbu: “Enywe abandu banje Nyasaye wanje shiyabalakakhwo indakano indayi? Koo ebise ebo bimurambiyile ebiamalakano ako nohomba mwenyele mbu lirumwa okhurula khu Nyasaye wenyu libeshele, khulwendio mufunache indakano yanje"